name: The End?
description:
Two very-friendly aliens discover that a giant asteroid is headed right for their planet! Can you help them delay the asteroid just long enough to fuel up their escape ship?

Make boosters at the factory and launch them at the asteroid to push it away (for a few extra seconds, at least).

Pump fuel at the fuel station and take it to the escape ship to prepare your getaway.

If you're quick enough, you might delay the inevitable just long enough to stay alive!

Controls

A/D: Green alien moves
W/S:  Green alien interacts

J/L: Yellow alien moves
I/K: Yellow alien interacts

Esc: Pause
